{"tid":2120472,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"又係化學撚叫春呀sorly...","createTime":"2020-07-22T17:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T17:25:32.000Z","uid":211274,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"15f1f940ae51563533fc4bc070191f317d26e8ca","tid":2120472,"uid":211274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:04:21.000Z","msg":"當初讀中學對化學好似幾有興趣，成績又幾好，<br />\n就鳩入咗三大晒銀時，揀咗化學<br />\n但讀讀下發現自己對化學其實唔係咁有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到上堂冇心機，爛撚晒grade<br />\n都冇諗過trans科..因為一嚟其實冇咩係真心想讀，二嚟個gpa絕對唔夠trans<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以諗住硬住頭皮讀完個degree就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想問下各位ching，讀完化學出嚟可以做啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔一定要本行嘅<br />\n同埋想知如果2nd low 或者3rd 考唔考到正苦工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb500afd0882ec6bc5a6e66e514e574806896ff1","tid":2120472,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"如果2nd low 或者3rd 考唔考到正苦工<br />\n<br />\n唔好話政府, 一般公司都未必請<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faa1e2b7a7b6a1bf3d74d0079ed4a582f8e3310","tid":2120472,"uid":198402,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cdf1abd9babb73e30686a32a5cb62c2abd04c3","tid":2120472,"uid":31818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:29:28.000Z","msg":"咪撚入行啦，除非你好撚有心讀上去，做個supervisor可能都係得20幾k (今年grad, 見過幾份lab 公價12k sor, 唔會入行）"},{"pid":"9bb26ed5cd20f5a1e0b0eeed8fd933055dc7c99c","tid":2120472,"uid":211274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58cdf1abd9babb73e30686a32a5cb62c2abd04c3","tid":2120472,"uid":31818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:29:28.000Z","msg":"咪撚入行啦，除非你好撚有